sentence: Financial shares are higher in today's pre-market session with no major data on tap and as Best Buy ( BBY ) and Home Depot ( HD ) report earnings.

In stocks news, Resource America ( REXI ) reports adjusted net income of $0.23 per common share-diluted and compared to adjusted net income attributable to common shareholders of $0.15 per common share-diluted in 2012.
Analysts expected $0.03 per share for Q3 on revenues of $15.6 million.
It's unclear if the earnings number is comparable.

And, Antony Leung, Blackstone Group LP ( BX )'s Greater China chairman, is stepping down to become Nan Fung Group Holdings Ltd.'s chief executive officer after seven years at the U.S. asset management firm, reports Bloomberg.
